Package org.aavso.tools.vstar.input.text

Class Summary
ObservationFieldSplitter This class splits an observation line given a delimiter.
ObservationSourceAnalyser This class analyses an observation file (simple or download formats) and makes information about the file available for use by consumers.
TextFormatObservationReader This class reads a variable star data file format containing lines of text or comma separated fields, and yields a collection of observations for one star.
